com.oracle.sfp.scripting.api.util

Interface IList<T>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Collection<T>, IScriptingObject, Iterable<T>, List<T>

    public interface IList<T>
extends List<T>, IScriptingObject
    This type enhances regular java/groovy List type with a few methods for backwards compatibility. Preferably, Groovy's own equivalent List enhancements (http://docs.groovy-lang.org/2.4.3/html/groovy-jdk/java/util/List.html) should be used.
